00:18:53,990 --> 00:18:56,071
I guess it was the money.

268
00:18:56,950 --> 00:18:59,687
You get a bonus if you find a scoop.

269
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:03,291
That's why?

270
00:19:05,430 --> 00:19:09,767
Okay, my reason is to expose the evil in this world with a single photo.

271
00:19:09,767 --> 00:19:11,917
Just drop it.

272
00:19:11,917 --> 00:19:13,917
I was kidding.

273
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:24,446
Let's see...

274
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:29,009
Maybe I was the same as you at first.

275
00:19:30,210 --> 00:19:31,518
What?

276
00:19:34,150 --> 00:19:36,017
It's nothing.

277
00:19:54,660 --> 00:19:58,396
Asaoka sure isn't coming out.

278
00:19:58,396 --> 00:20:00,155
Yeah.

279
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:04,590
[Weekly Dash!]

280
00:20:05,170 --> 00:20:07,624
Hey, isn't that...

281
00:20:09,220 --> 00:20:11,304
This is the issue where I got the cover story.

282
00:20:11,304 --> 00:20:13,655
Don't touch my stuff.

283
00:20:13,655 --> 00:20:16,379
What? You've been researching me?

284
00:20:16,379 --> 00:20:18,356
What are you talking about?

285
00:20:18,356 --> 00:20:21,186
I saw the "Dash!" in your bag.

286
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,745
You're just seeing things.

287
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,321
Hey, it's Asaoka!

288
00:20:27,321 --> 00:20:28,668
What?

289
00:20:30,565 --> 00:20:33,754
See? I knew it.

290
00:20:33,754 --> 00:20:36,663
You went out of your way to read it.

291
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:55,709
You're such a pain.

292
00:20:55,709 --> 00:20:57,269
Sorry.

293
00:21:03,910 --> 00:21:05,390
He's here.

294
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:12,659
They won't get closer.

295
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:18,913
Come on, get closer!

296
00:21:18,913 --> 00:21:21,877
Yes, just a bit closer...

297
00:21:33,980 --> 00:21:36,837
He left.

298
00:21:40,870 --> 00:21:44,017
This won't work as a scoop.

299
00:21:49,620 --> 00:21:54,641
Hey, can you zoom in on that guy's face?

300
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:03,574
I might know this guy.

301
00:22:03,574 --> 00:22:05,410
What do you mean?

302
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:07,960
Who was it?

303
00:22:08,630 --> 00:22:10,560
I saw him somewhere.

304
00:22:14,650 --> 00:22:16,368
Hey, who is he?

305
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:20,920
Mano Kosei of the Otsuka Crime Syndicate.

306
00:22:22,630 --> 00:22:24,479
From the yakuza?

307
00:22:24,479 --> 00:22:26,527
You even knew his name?

308
00:22:26,527 --> 00:22:29,612
There was a bribery scandal in the government last year.

309
00:22:29,612 --> 00:22:33,732
They discovered a lot of illegal activity from this group,

310
00:22:33,732 --> 00:22:36,107
and their leader was arrested.

311
00:22:36,107 --> 00:22:38,948
Mano was his direct aide.

312
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:42,804
Now I get it.

313
00:22:42,804 --> 00:22:44,231
What?

314
00:22:45,360 --> 00:22:47,940
The Otsuka group has connections everywhere.

315
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:50,791
Even in the entertainment industry.

316
00:22:50,791 --> 00:22:54,604
Asaoka Yumi gets a lot of commercial deals

317
00:22:54,604 --> 00:22:57,213
because of the Otsuka group.

318
00:22:57,900 --> 00:23:03,188
The commercial queen is linked with the yakuza.

319
00:23:03,188 --> 00:23:06,818
This scoop is even bigger than adultery.

320
00:23:08,620 --> 00:23:12,110
Yeah, great work.

321
00:23:14,540 --> 00:23:16,113
What is it?

322
00:23:17,930 --> 00:23:21,489
You... know how to smile?

323
00:23:22,540 --> 00:23:24,815
Of course, I do.

324
00:23:24,815 --> 00:23:28,080
But hey, you're amazing.

325
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:35,330
Timing and Subtitles brought to you

326
00:23:35,330 --> 00:23:39,384
Why is my heart beating so fast?

327
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:45,015
Calm down. Calm down.

328
00:23:45,015 --> 00:23:48,056
[Preview]
You've fallen for Kaburagi.

329
00:23:48,056 --> 00:23:50,683
I'll look for Otsuka group's Mano when he comes out.

330
00:23:50,683 --> 00:23:52,453
But I preferred this before in case of emergencies.

331
00:23:52,453 --> 00:23:54,211
I might've been wrong.

332
00:23:54,211 --> 00:23:56,345
You should change teams

333
00:23:56,345 --> 00:23:57,971
before you become numb like me.

334
00:23:57,972 --> 00:23:59,982
You're a nice guy.
[This story is completely fiction]
